What I Learned in PsychologyScenario #1Gerard Mr. Gerard Way has been the front man for My Chemical Romance for some time now. His band has collected many fans of the years young and old; a variety of people relate to the bands music. Mr. Gerard Way has even said himself that the band has the best fans in the world. But with the good always comes the bad One glorious afternoon, Mr. Gerard is walking along. He has taken a break from the band as have the other band members. My Chemical Romance is on hiatus. He walks along the sidewalk when all of a sudden there is a squeal of his name. His head lifts and he is on alert but it is too late. Mr. Gerard Way is, unfortunately, mobbed by a group of teenybopper girls. They scream his name and ask for him to marry them. The girls pull at his jacket and his hair. After getting them off his back, he is quite shaken and upset. Later along in the year his band resumes its musical greatness.
